      <abstract id="aspace_986102f92efc0d59a6e629cba1132101">A letter from Sineus Hopping to his parents, dated November 1, 1862. The letter was written by Hopping while aboard the United States Receiving Ship North Carolina at the Brooklyn Navy Yard. In the letter, Hopping discusses his impending incription into the military. Hopping was from Bridgehampton, Long Island.</abstract>
